WEBVTT

00:06:33.680 --> 00:06:37.736
He fell in love with the music instantly,

00:06:37.760 --> 00:06:39.816
but he had to know
the backstory behind it.

00:06:39.840 --> 00:06:41.560
He didn't know where it came from.

00:06:42.760 --> 00:06:44.016
He knew the artist,

00:06:44.040 --> 00:06:45.456
at the time of the recording,

00:06:45.480 --> 00:06:46.736
was living in Montreal,

00:06:46.760 --> 00:06:48.760
so for months, he tried to track him down.

00:06:49.520 --> 00:06:53.120
He even found Noël's business card
inside the record sleeve.

00:06:53.640 --> 00:06:57.160
That's how DIY Henri-Pierre Noël was.

00:06:57.680 --> 00:07:01.176
So he found the card
inside the record sleeve --